# Aegis Assault Game Design
1. Rail Shooter
	a. Players	- move horizontal/vertical
	b. Camera	- moves on a rail/path and limits player movement
	c. Enemies	- flies on path or stationary; might shoot
2. Player Experience	- chaotic
3. Core Mechanics		- dodge and shoot
4. Core Game Loop		- get as far as possible without dying to obtain highest score; start from beginning when died

# Level Beat Chart
1. There will be 4 phases:
	1. Intro - easy obstacle
	2. Stage 1 - easy enemies
	3. Stage 2 - cool down and collect information
	4. Stage 3 - Intense af
